      "props": {
        "variant": "body"
      },
      "content": "**Endpoint:** `POST /v1/payment/refunds/process`\n\nInitiates a refund against a completed card payment. Vesicash queues the reversal and routes it through the card network back to the customer's card issuer.\n\n---",
      "meta": {}
